Hnydf3e3X-w.title: THAI KING CORONATION 2019 | พระราชพิธีบรมราชาภิเษก
Hnydf3e3X-w.description:
THAI KING CORONATION 2019 | พระราชพิธีบรมราชาภิเษก | King Maha Vajiralongkorn coronation in Bangkok Thailand 2019. King Vajiralongkorn is The King of Thailand and we were in Bangkok for the King's Coronation Parade on 5th May 2019. 

ขอบคุณสำหรับการติดตามรับชม
พระราชพิธีบรมราชาภิเษก﻿
Ceremonies are underway in Bangkok to crown Thailand's new King Maha Vajiralongkorn. Also known as Rama the Tenth, the king was officially crowned as a divine monarch, the first the country has seen in seven decades. The 66-year-old ascended to the throne after the death of his widely-revered father, Bhumibol Adulyadej, in 2016. Saturday's pageantry is the start of a three-day ceremony that formally invests him with regal power, symbolizing his consecration as the upholder of Buddhism in Thailand. The ceremony included a purification ritual, with sacred waters from throughout Thailand and Bangkok and the coronation of the new king and Queen Suthida.

Ya66PcetJ6M.title: ROSS BARKLEY WEAK FOOT CHALLENGE! ROY'S ROAD TO THE EUROS #2
Ya66PcetJ6M.description:
Welcome to the first Official Episode of Roy's Road to the Euros. Today's episode focuses on Everton FC including the Ross Barkley Weak Foot Challenge that Andy sent me in. 

Andy's Channel - https://goo.gl/gQceDS

Thanks to Simon for Flying his Drone for us! I film a lot with Simon over on my GeorgeBensonVlogs channel! Check Him out and go Subscribe!

Simon 
YouTube - https://www.youtube.com/user/STOPJABBAINGON
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/stopjabbaingon/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/stopjabbaingon

New Vlog Channel Video - https://goo.gl/bFNfgk

Roy's Road to the Euros Rules:
1. Each Episode is focused on One Premier League Club..
2. I play 3 matches per episode, each match gives me the opportunity to unlock 1 player from the club.
3. Draws, losses mean I cannot unlock the player, but count towards the progression up the Online Season divisions as we look to get into Division 1.
4. For each episode, the key player from the club can be unlocked by completing a Football based challenge, related to that player.
5. If I succeed, that player is unlocked and therefore I am able to use that Ultimate Team card in the series.
6. If I do not unlock any of the four players available per episode, they become available again in 5 episodes time. It is up to you guys to decide whether we play extra FUT matches to unlock them, or have another Football based challenge in order to Unlock this player.
